data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom berm home in a prime location offers an open floor-plan, making it perfect. The spacious living areas, including the living room, dining area, and kitchen, create an ideal space for entertaining. Enjoy the convenience of two full bathrooms and ample natural light throughout the home. The well-appointed kitchen, fenced in backyard, and two-car garage add to the appeal. With energy-efficient features, this home combines style and sustainability, making it a rare find. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
